dataList.content: <You think all of these shipping containers are full of...>
Right... Let's try to not linger on that thought.
I tried my best to not speculate about what terrible things the pirates might be hiding in that mountain of shipping containers.

dataList.title: Twinhook Pirates?
dataList.content: Hey! Who's there? How'd ya find this place?!
Ah, hey, we're just here to check out that shipping container with a green triangle over here~ And we'll be right outta your hair, 'kay?
<Let's take them out before anything worse happens to our Agent...>
